        <h2>HTML Helpers</h2>
        <p>
            HtmlHelper class generates html elements using the model class
            object in razor view. It binds the model object to html elements
            to display value of model properties into html elements and also
            assigns the value of the html elements to the model properties
            while submitting web form. So always use HtmlHelper class in razor
            view instead of writing html tags manually.
        </p>
